import React from "react";

import FormCSS from './styles/Form.module.css'

export default function Form() {
    return (<>
        <form action="">
            <textarea className={FormCSS.textarea} name="textQUE" placeholder="Введите текст вопроса"></textarea>

            <label>Выберите тип ответа:
                <label><input type="radio" name="type" />example</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="type" />example</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="type" />example</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="type" />example</label>
            </label>
        </form>
    </>)
}
